curriculum /kəˈrɪkjʊləm/

(curricula/kəˈrɪkjələ/) 

1. N-COUNT A curriculum is all the different courses of study that are taught in a school, college, or university. 总课程 

例： Teachers incorporated business skills into the regular school curriculum. 教师们将商业技能纳入学校常规课程。 

2. N-COUNT A particular curriculum is one particular course of study that is taught in a school, college, or university. 课程 

例： ...the history curriculum. …历史课程。

</div>

